                                                            ✨99 Names of Allah (Al Asma Ul Husna)✨

🌸 Pehla Imaan ka Sutoon (Pillar of Iman):
👉 Allah par imaan lana.
Musalmaan ke liye zaroori hai ke woh Allah ko uske khoobsurat Asma (names) aur Sifaat (attributes) ke zariye pehchaane.
💡 Qur’an mein Allah Ta’ala ne apne naam bar bar zikr kiye taa ke hum usko samajh saken aur uske saath sahi rishte banayein – 
  mohabbat ❤️, khauf 😨, umeed 🌟, aur bharosa 🤲.                                                            

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

📖 Qur’an ke Ayaat:

1️⃣ “Aur Allah ke liye sabse ache naam hain, to usko unhi naamon se pukaro.”
(Qur’an 7:180)

2️⃣ “Allah – uske siwa koi ma’bood nahi. Uske liye sabse ache naam hain.”
(Qur’an 20:8)

3️⃣ “Wohi Allah hai, Khaaliq (Creator) 🪐, Baari (Inventor) 🛠️, Musawwir (Fashioner 🎨). Uske liye sabse khoobsurat naam hain.”
(Qur’an 59:24)

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌹 Hadees (ﷺ):

🕌 Nabi ﷺ ne farmaya:
“Allah ke 99 naam hain, jo shakhs inhe yaad karega (samajh kar aur amal karega) woh Jannat mein daakhil hoga.”
(Sahih Bukhari 54:23)

✨ Abu Hurairah (RA) riwayat karte hain:
“Allah ke 99 naam hain. Jo banda inhe yaad kare (hifz kare aur samajh kar amal kare) woh Jannat mein daakhil hoga. 
Yaqeenan Allah Witr (Odd) hai, aur Allah ko odd numbers pasand hain.”
(Sahih Muslim Book 48 Hadith 5)

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

💭 Sochne ki baat:
Hum Allah se mohabbat kaise karenge 💖, usse darenge kaise 😢, aur us par bharosa kaise rakhenge 🤲 agar hum usko pehchaante hi na ho?
👉 Is liye Asma Ul Husna seekhna aur samajhna imaan ka buniyadi hissa hai.
